      "title": "Modi's statement on Indian aid to Sri Lanka at the G7 Summit",
      "author": "Rajeeban",
      "body_lines": [
        "Narendra Modi has said that India is taking steps to ensure Sri Lanka's food security.",
        "\"We have been sending wheat to neighboring Afghanistan as humanitarian aid for the past few months. India was the first to provide emergency aid after the earthquake."
